Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Killing the Inward Dragon
By: Swami Sivananda
---
Be a hero on the battlefield of the Absolute (adhyâtmâ). Be a fearless
soldier of the spirit. The inward battle against the mind, the
senses, the subconscious impregnations (vâsanâs) and the residues of
anterior states (samskâras) is more terrible than outward battle.
